MARRIAGE MEETING, WON'T I?

36
00:02:48,333 --> 00:02:52,541
- Kamidake: YES, PRINCESS, BUT--
- I KNOW, YES, IT IS MY DUTY

37
00:02:52,625 --> 00:02:55,500
AS THE FIRST PRINCESS 
OF JURAI ROYAL FAMILY.

38
00:02:58,458 --> 00:03:01,458
YES, I KNOW IT
TOO WELL.

39
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:06,833
- ( man howls )

40
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:12,833
- HEY, TENCHI. COME ON,
TENCHI, LET'S GO PLAY.

41
00:03:12,916 --> 00:03:14,583
YOUR SILLY CHORES
ARE BORING.

42
00:03:14,666 --> 00:03:16,875
- ALL RIGHT,
THAT'S ENOUGH.

43
00:03:16,958 --> 00:03:20,416
YOU KNOW GRANDPA'S VERY FUSSY
ABOUT KEEPING THE SHRINE CLEAN.

44
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:23,125
- ( hums )

45
00:03:23,208 --> 00:03:24,875
- HUH?

46
00:03:24,958 --> 00:03:26,916
MIHOSHI, WHAT IS THAT THING?

47
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,125
- A SPECIAL DEVICE
MADE EXCLUSIVELY

48
00:03:29,208 --> 00:03:30,250
FOR THE GALAXY POLICE.

49
00:03:30,333 --> 00:03:33,583
YOU TURN IT THIS WAY
AND THAT WAY.

50
00:03:33,666 --> 00:03:36,708
THERE!  I CAN SEND OUT
A DISTRESS SIGNAL NOW.

51
00:03:36,791 --> 00:03:38,250
- WE'RE IN THE BOONIES, KIDDO.

52
00:03:38,333 --> 00:03:40,125
CAN YOU REALLY COUNT
ON A TOY LIKE THAT? 

53
00:03:40,208 --> 00:03:42,250
- ACCORDING TO 
THE STATISTICS,

54
