IS REPORTED TO RESULT

55
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:46,833
IN SUCCESSFUL RESCUE.

56
00:03:46,916 --> 00:03:49,291
- YEAH, RIGHT.
THAT'S WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

57
00:03:49,375 --> 00:03:51,791
- ( gong rings )
- ( whimpers )

58
00:03:51,875 --> 00:03:53,958
( cries )
WELL, IT'S BETTER THAN

59
