409
00:22:41,250 --> 00:22:44,833
♪ WHAT MORE CAN I SAY ♪

410
00:22:44,916 --> 00:22:46,375
♪ I'LL GET THE GUY ♪

411
00:22:46,458 --> 00:22:51,000
♪ HE'LL HOLD ME CLOSE
TO THE VERY END OF TIME ♪

412
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:52,750
♪ WHEN YOU LOSE ♪

413
00:22:52,833 --> 00:22:54,666
♪ HOW YOU WILL 
