414
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:59,250
♪ 'CAUSE THE GUY
WILL BE MINE. ♪ 

415
00:23:25,208 --> 00:23:26,458
- Tenchi:
"TENCHI MUYO."

416
00:23:26,541 --> 00:23:28,291
THE NEXT AND THE FIFTH
IN LINE TO JOIN OUR FAMILY

417
00:23:28,375 --> 00:23:30,125
IS SASAMI,
AYEKA'S LITTLE SISTER.

418
00:23:30,208 --> 00:23:32,458
THIS BRAVE LITTLE GIRL
HAS TRAVELLED FAR TO EARTH

419
00:23:32,541 --> 00:23:35,000
IN SEARCH OF HER
MISSING SISTER AYEKA.

420
00:23:35,083 --> 00:23:37,541
AH? WHAT IS THIS
CAT-LIKE CREATURE?

421
00:23:37,625 --> 00:23:39,125
WHAT? RYO-OHKI?

