00:23:39,208 --> 00:23:41,750
BUT I THOUGHT RYO-OHKI WAS
THE NAME OF RYOKO'S SPACESHIP.

423
00:23:41,833 --> 00:23:44,625
"NO NEED FOR WORRIES"
IS COMING NEXT.

424
00:23:44,708 --> 00:23:46,666
- Ryoko:
SHE'S UNDISPUTABLY CUTE.

